    "plan_content": "Here's a summary of the plan I've prepared:\n\n## Plan: `CosineAnnealingScheduler`\n\n**4 files total — 2 new, 2 edited. No optional dependencies beyond torch.**\n\n### New files\n\n**`src/diffusers/schedulers/scheduling_cosine_annealing.py`**\nModels after `scheduling_ddpm.py`. The beta schedule is computed as:\n```python\nt = torch.arange(T, dtype=torch.float32)\nbetas = beta_start + 0.5 * (beta_end - beta_start) * (1.0 + torch.cos(math.pi * t / T))\n```\n- At t=0: `betas[0] = beta_end` (max noise) ✓\n- At t=T-1: `betas[-1] ≈ beta_start` (min noise) ✓\n- Monotonically non-increasing ✓\n\nImplements all required methods: `set_timesteps`, `step` (DDPM-style reverse SDE with epsilon/sample/v_prediction + fixed_small variance), `add_noise`, `scale_model_input`, `previous_timestep`, `_get_variance`, `_threshold_sample`, `__len__`. Defines `CosineAnnealingSchedulerOutput(BaseOutput)`.\n\n**`tests/schedulers/test_scheduler_cosine_annealing.py`**\nInherits `SchedulerCommonTest` (10+ free tests). Custom tests: beta formula verification, alphas_cumprod monotonicity, variance values, all prediction types, custom timestep edge cases, and a full denoising loop test (empirical expected values obtained on first run before hardcoding).\n\n### Edits to existing files\n\n**`src/diffusers/schedulers/__init__.py`** — 2 insertions (alphabetically after `scheduling_consistency_models`):\n- Add to `_import_structure` dict\n- Add to `TYPE_CHECKING` import block\n\n**`src/diffusers/__init__.py`** — 2 insertions (between `CMStochasticIterativeScheduler` and `CogVideoXDDIMScheduler`):\n- Add to `_import_structure[\"schedulers\"].extend([...])` list (~line 344)\n- Add to `TYPE_CHECKING` import block (~line 1115)",
